{"tid":1494540,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國玩家有褔了] Steam China命名”蒸氣平台”！將為獨立運作地區？","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T18:51:30.000Z","uid":90259,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db2acae541238a66138dba4136d6cf3a6b3b3a43","tid":1494540,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"據外媒消息指出，在8月21日的Steam China 媒體試玩會上，Valve的中國合作夥伴完美世界對外正式宣布中國版Steam將定名&rdquo;蒸氣平台&rdquo;。<br />\n外媒轉述他們提到，蒸氣平台將專門為中國玩家打造，提供高速伺服器，高質量 (素？)本地化等服務，重點是：蒸氣平台幾乎完全獨立於Steam。首批上架的遊戲有Dota2等Valve自家遊戲，暫時只有近[red]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">40</span>[/green]款&hellip;但官方表示遊戲庫會在日後繼續擴充，並包括VR遊戲，讓中國玩家繼續等待更多新消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3igame.com/steam-china命名蒸氣平台！將為獨立運作地區？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2Fsteam-china%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E8%92%B8%E6%B0%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%87%E7%82%BA%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn05mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=6fe7e4f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.3igame.com/steam-china命名蒸氣平台！將為獨立運作地區？/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technode.com/2019/08/21/steam-china-will-be-separate-from-the-international-version-of-steam/?fbclid=IwAR21SBCbpJFnjxT4V425WULMbEAyKU136k1Fe2h4GUH6RdvMyxfYfqy0mpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnode.com%2F2019%2F08%2F21%2Fsteam-china-will-be-separate-from-the-international-version-of-steam%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR21SBCbpJFnjxT4V425WULMbEAyKU136k1Fe2h4GUH6RdvMyxfYfqy0mpg&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn05mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=9ff302fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://technode.com/2019/08/21/steam-china-will-be-separate-from-the-international-version-of-steam/?fbclid=IwAR21SBCbpJFnjxT4V425WULMbEAyKU136k1Fe2h4GUH6RdvMyxfYfqy0mpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8VRLYq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8VRLYq.jpg&h=4bff32ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以由廣電總局精心挑選優秀遊戲，又有國家從旁關懷<br />\n其他國家都冇嘅恨死人超規格獨立待遇<br />\n廣大中國玩家依家應該感動流涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fa95520b46d5e447a4a69a651bdb0b4bed67d8","tid":1494540,"uid":147890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"做中國人連玩遊戲既自由都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8a5702adc8760ae88b6a0aecf5fcb2dd453d66","tid":1494540,"uid":90259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"順便一提，大陸steam用家大部分對人對呢個中國獨立平台冇乜大反應<br />\n因為佢地相信官方講steam同蒸氣平台會同時並存，國內兩種制度係獨立唔會互相影響或取代<br />\n大陸玩家覺得唔會燒到自己，機照打game照買<br />\n<br />\n啲對白同情景係咪好熟口熟面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d069256e1ed93f48edd19454707f4c7692284894","tid":1494540,"uid":20518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:48:52.000Z","msg":"諗起大陸steam就諗起mhw單野<br />\n<br />\n個個買企鵝版以為自己高人一等睇唔起steam版，結果企鵝版唔更新成班人死死地氣買多份steam版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc70549b3896e7f2b56576e53d217fa3939fd69","tid":1494540,"uid":67771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"如果真係有個專屬蒸氣平台，實在非常光榮，忍唔住叫一句chi na"},{"pid":"f02505570ae34ea067038fc17c8ec84a17426976","tid":1494540,"uid":61853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b8a5702adc8760ae88b6a0aecf5fcb2dd453d66","tid":1494540,"uid":90259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"順便一提，大陸steam用家大部分對人對呢個中國獨立平台冇乜大反應<br />\n因為佢地相信官方講steam同蒸氣平台會同時並存，國內兩種制度係獨立唔會互相影響或取代<br />\n大陸玩家覺得唔會燒到自己，機照打game照買<br />\n<br />\n啲對白同情景係咪好熟口熟面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl